# AI-Influenced Slangs in 2026

AI tools changed internet language dramatically.

## Promptmaxxing

**Meaning:** Trying to master AI prompts for better results.

### Example:
> “He spent 3 hours promptmaxxing ChatGPT.”

---

## Botposting

**Meaning:** Content that feels AI-generated or fake.

### Example:
> “That LinkedIn post is pure botposting.”

---

## GPT Brain

**Meaning:** Relying too much on AI for thinking or writing.

### Example:
> “I forgot how to write emails. I got GPT brain.”

